01:10:07.295 --> 01:10:08.155
during the Miqrah.

01:10:08.716 --> 01:10:11.557
And since there was a prophetic reference

01:10:11.957 --> 01:10:14.380
elsewhere to the Ruach pertaining to an

01:10:14.460 --> 01:10:17.322
illuminating apparel in Yasha'yah,

01:10:17.341 --> 01:10:17.862
I thought, well,

01:10:17.942 --> 01:10:20.283
perhaps that's how God resolved the issue

01:10:20.323 --> 01:10:22.425
of our guilt, covering us with it,

01:10:22.484 --> 01:10:26.108
projecting this onto the symbolism of the

01:10:26.148 --> 01:10:26.368
fire.

01:10:29.328 --> 01:10:29.769
However,

01:10:30.149 --> 01:10:32.890
matzah is not about the addition of

01:10:32.930 --> 01:10:33.329
something,

01:10:34.670 --> 01:10:37.470
but instead the removal of the

01:10:37.511 --> 01:10:41.072
contaminating fungus of yeast representing

01:10:41.572 --> 01:10:42.872
religious and political guilt.

01:10:42.912 --> 01:10:44.551
It's not covered over with light.

01:10:45.233 --> 01:10:46.932
It's taken into the ultimate darkness.

01:10:49.332 --> 01:10:51.092
So the moment I came to realize that

01:10:51.153 --> 01:10:53.292
Do's Bashar body fulfilled Pesach,

01:10:53.693 --> 01:10:55.033
opening the door to life,

01:10:55.094 --> 01:10:56.993
making him the tree of lives,

01:10:57.595 --> 01:11:00.194
and that his nephesh soul, feminine,

01:11:00.735 --> 01:11:02.435
carried our guilt away,

01:11:02.716 --> 01:11:06.377
depositing it in the darkness of Sheowl on

01:11:06.476 --> 01:11:08.717
Matzah, never to be seen again,

01:11:09.177 --> 01:11:11.219
my conjecture regarding the spirit's

01:11:11.338 --> 01:11:14.439
requirement of light became unnecessary

01:11:14.479 --> 01:11:14.760
clutter.

01:11:17.579 --> 01:11:18.020
Similarly,

01:11:18.400 --> 01:11:19.922
I came to realize that I had been

01:11:19.962 --> 01:11:23.126
wrong regarding the Ruach departing from

01:11:23.206 --> 01:11:25.068
Dowd during his fulfillment of the Miqrah.

01:11:25.087 --> 01:11:27.470
That's what I read into.

01:11:27.530 --> 01:11:28.311
My God, my God,

01:11:28.351 --> 01:11:29.552
why have you forsaken me?

01:11:29.953 --> 01:11:32.176
But it's Yahowah separating from his son,

01:11:32.216 --> 01:11:32.877
not the spirit.

01:11:34.516 --> 01:11:36.957
Yahowah told us explicitly when the Ruach

01:11:36.997 --> 01:11:38.537
came upon his son, Dowd,

01:11:38.957 --> 01:11:39.978
that he would never leave,

01:11:40.198 --> 01:11:42.279
would never separate from him, ever.

01:11:42.779 --> 01:11:44.819
And this means that the Ruach protected

01:11:44.880 --> 01:11:48.480
Dowd's nephesh in Sheowl and facilitated his

01:11:48.541 --> 01:11:51.041
release.

01:11:51.121 --> 01:11:53.582
Now, this realization leads to another.

01:11:54.122 --> 01:11:56.643
Since the spirit entered Sheowl,

01:11:57.042 --> 01:11:58.682
the place of separation from God,

01:11:59.042 --> 01:12:01.264
the Ruach cannot be Yahowah.

01:12:02.179 --> 01:12:04.702
but instead is a manifestation of his

01:12:04.782 --> 01:12:09.487
influence, a projection of his power,

01:12:09.567 --> 01:12:12.529
of his protection.

01:12:12.550 --> 01:12:14.872
The spirit of Yahowah is the most powerful

01:12:14.931 --> 01:12:16.453
and capable tool in the universe.

01:12:17.073 --> 01:12:19.476
Yahowah sent his Ruach,

01:12:19.577 --> 01:12:21.578
the spirit of Yahowah,

01:12:23.161 --> 01:12:25.203
to reside within the Choter.

01:12:26.121 --> 01:12:28.322
That does not make the Choter Yahowah.

01:12:28.942 --> 01:12:31.023
It does not make the Choter a girly

01:12:31.042 --> 01:12:32.003
version of Yahowah.

01:12:32.583 --> 01:12:34.064
It doesn't make the Choter a mother.

01:12:36.105 --> 01:12:38.867
The spirit of Yahowah is a projection of

01:12:39.266 --> 01:12:45.550
Yahowah's influence, his protection.

01:12:45.609 --> 01:12:46.310
It's not God.

01:12:46.430 --> 01:12:54.394
The spirit of Yahowah is the most powerful

01:12:54.814 --> 01:12:55.675
and capable tool

01:12:56.854 --> 01:13:00.676
the universe now as for the isha fire

01:13:01.237 --> 01:13:02.837
there was a far better interpretation

01:13:02.856 --> 01:13:05.018
providing a lesson for us all fire

01:13:05.057 --> 01:13:07.759
transforms dead and dying organic material

01:13:08.100 --> 01:13:10.541
and transforming it into light and radiant

01:13:10.600 --> 01:13:11.980
energy I've shared this on so many of

01:13:12.020 --> 01:13:14.442
our programs it is symbolic of the

01:13:14.521 --> 01:13:17.143
superior vessel that Yahowah intends for

01:13:17.182 --> 01:13:20.204
our souls so that we can discard the

01:13:20.284 --> 01:13:22.525
limiting and decaying nature of our

01:13:22.565 --> 01:13:23.326
physical bodies

01:13:23.786 --> 01:13:26.189
When our nephesh is encapsulated in

01:13:26.269 --> 01:13:27.569
radiant energy and light,

01:13:27.970 --> 01:13:30.073
we are not only perfected and become

01:13:30.233 --> 01:13:32.576
immortal, we are enabled, we're empowered,

01:13:32.615 --> 01:13:33.377
we're enriched.

01:13:34.137 --> 01:13:36.600
By such a great magnitude in science,

01:13:36.659 --> 01:13:39.023
this transformation is measured in the

01:13:39.103 --> 01:13:40.625
square of the speed of light.

01:13:41.960 --> 01:13:44.881
So this progression from a thoughtful

01:13:44.942 --> 01:13:48.685
interpretation to a vastly superior and

01:13:48.784 --> 01:13:51.987
evidenced comprehension of Yahowah's

01:13:52.027 --> 01:13:55.250
methodology comes with observation and

01:13:55.289 --> 01:13:58.252
contemplation, hard work,

01:13:59.295 --> 01:14:00.735
building over decades.

01:14:01.095 --> 01:14:03.398
And the beauty of this process is that

01:14:03.978 --> 01:14:05.680
it becomes exponential.

01:14:06.079 --> 01:14:07.541
The more we know and understand,

01:14:07.560 --> 01:14:10.203
the better we are equipped to deduce a

01:14:10.403 --> 01:14:13.265
myriad of previously unseen insights and

01:14:13.324 --> 01:14:15.907
grow in our comprehension of God and then

01:14:15.947 --> 01:14:17.948
become much more productive as that tree

01:14:17.988 --> 01:14:18.488
of knowledge.

01:14:20.471 --> 01:14:22.434
So after having written thirty-five books

01:14:22.873 --> 01:14:25.815
based upon uniquely amplified translations

01:14:25.876 --> 01:14:28.278
of the oldest extant resources,

01:14:28.797 --> 01:14:33.021
with words scribed and scrubbed of man's

01:14:33.082 --> 01:14:34.342
religious corruptions,

01:14:35.884 --> 01:14:39.247
I've come to learn more about God than

01:14:39.306 --> 01:14:41.148
anyone since the last of the prophets

01:14:41.188 --> 01:14:45.150
twenty-five centuries ago.

01:14:45.171 --> 01:14:46.851
There were thousands of profound and

01:14:47.012 --> 01:14:48.613
unheralded insights to share.

01:14:50.065 --> 01:14:52.188
with the proper pronunciation of Yahowah's

01:14:52.247 --> 01:14:54.609
name and the recognition of his son's

01:14:54.649 --> 01:14:56.331
achievement foremost among them.

01:14:58.412 --> 01:15:00.274
And as my knowledge and understanding

01:15:00.333 --> 01:15:00.835
progressed,

01:15:02.536 --> 01:15:08.100
these books were augmented and refined.

01:15:08.199 --> 01:15:09.681
I think we'll conclude this program at

01:15:09.702 --> 01:15:10.101
this point.

01:15:20.755 --> 01:15:21.503
Thank you for listening.

